title: DCC 24KT Gold GZS 1020 - 1035 PACK #1 ALAC
description:
This is the first of 8 packs of the DCC Compact classics collection. It is only missing six. These are all mastered by Steve Hoffman. The last pack will contain the artwork and a few of the CD's. The 10 cc Album is an unreleased one. However it is known that at least a few hundred came out that were just in the jewel case without any artwork. I believe the one here is from one of those and because it had no artwork I have just used the disc image as the artwork.

Here is a list of the ones missing and I hope that someone will be able to upload these to complete the collection for all.

GZS 1102	Bill Evans Trio		Interplay

GZS 1104	Nat King Cole		Love is the thing

GZS 1130	Judy Collins		Colors of the day /best of

GZS 1135-2	Judy Garland		Judy at Carnegie Hall

GZS 1141	Everly Brothers		Best of

ARZ 104-2	Sinatra			Robin and the 7 Hoods


Please seed! Not for me because I have them but because it is the right thing to do
